{"tid":2298631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國政府提新法案　使用華為設備企業將被每日罰款10萬英鎊","createTime":"2020-11-24T07:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:34:00.000Z","uid":227801,"like":116,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5b8e99a23da12a4190a0ef43135c7f5e901f46","tid":2298631,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414083&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e1e0d917\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414083&h=3fa3d18f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414083</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】英國政府向國會提出新法案，違例使用華為設備的英國電訊商將會被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n英國已要求英國電訊商，在2027年前逐步淘汰華為5G設備。<br />\n<br />\n根據新的《通訊（安全）法案》，違例企業最高將被罰款營業額一成或每日10萬英鎊，即折合約103萬港元，若獲得通過將在2024年實施。"},{"pid":"9784ed1111647283f3d6f960035242d6a155c626","tid":2298631,"uid":180293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"我地支那幫手比!"},{"pid":"3cf4815ad90b779d01030dcc12913cdbf49903e0","tid":2298631,"uid":32782,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"9784ed1111647283f3d6f960035242d6a155c626","tid":2298631,"uid":180293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"我地支那幫手比!"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"真係唔出奇 一年都係3.65億 d資料都值唔至呢個價"},{"pid":"f2f8250309be1bcb9407fbd22807003a7706c65b","tid":2298631,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj